These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, reading
The people have 2 different jobs:  photographer, engineer
1. the photographer is in an even position##4
2. the engineer is the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Hobby   | reading | traveling |
| Job     | engineer    | photographer   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: sprite, lemonade
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, tennis
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Beverage   | lemonade | sprite        |
| Sport      | rowing  | tennis |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: french, thai
1. the french is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of rock is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Music-Genre   | rock    | folk |
| Nationality   | french | thai |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, sprite
There 2 different types of food: plum, potato
1. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate      | sprite |
| Food       | plum | potato    |

 #################################

 
