.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-10::.
There 2 different types of food: apricot, watermelon
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: blues, punk
1. the fan of punk is the person eating watermelon##1
2. the fan of blues is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |     2     |
| Food          | watermelon | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | punk | blues   |

