The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, biathlon
1. the indian is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left or right of the spanish##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Nationality   | indian | spanish   |
| Sport         | lacrosse | biathlon |

